  <brief_title>A 24-week Off-drug Extension Study in Sarcopenic Elderly Who Completed Treatment in the 6-month Core Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 24-week Off Drug Extension Parallel Group Study Assessing the Durability of Effect on Skeletal Muscle Strength and Function Following a 6-month Double-blind Placebo-controlled Study Evaluating Bimagrumab in Older Adults With Sarcopenia</official_title>
