  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A 24-week off drug extension parallel group study assessing the durability of effect on
      skeletal muscle strength and function following a 6-month double-blind placebo-controlled
      study evaluating bimagrumab in older adults with sarcopenia
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective is to assess the durability of effect of bimagrumab (BYM338) as
      measured by the short physical performance battery (SPPB) total score at week 49.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
